The paper discusses deep learning theory from the perspective of dynamical systems and optimal control. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as it discusses the application of control theory to optimization algorithms. cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper mentions information bottleneck theory. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is relevant as the paper discusses deep neural networks. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also relevant as the paper discusses different learning problems and their extensions.
